00:34:30.335 --> 00:34:32.036
Your accident. It sounds awful.

543
00:34:32.103 --> 00:34:33.539
T-boned by a car?

544
00:34:33.605 --> 00:34:35.241
Intra-cranial bleed?

545
00:34:35.306 --> 00:34:37.743
Death-defying surgery?

546
00:34:37.842 --> 00:34:39.378
